Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.92,0:00:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.82,0:00:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罪恶为此而戴上了面具\N希望能以此错误
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.70,0:00:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,换取持续戮力不停\N所追求的真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.71,0:00:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为命运而不知所措之\N叹息的玫瑰念珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.34,0:00:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因无法抹去的记忆\N而为爱颤抖着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.39,0:01:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当月光照亮黑夜之时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.12,0:01:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,传说促使得宇宙舞动着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.19,0:01:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虚幻的坠天使们啊\N美丽的飞翔吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.40,0:01:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在禁忌的决斗展开时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.84,0:01:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死神正自遥远的地方呼喊着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.02,0:01:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第二话重力的使命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.02,0:02:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是真实的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.59,0:02:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神机超重神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.96,0:02:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.03,0:02:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,与美丽同时兼具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.29,0:02:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是人类的希望!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.30,0:02:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,简直是神话般的景象啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.60,0:02:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太不可思议了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.80,0:02:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太平洋舰队已进入备战状态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.04,0:02:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总统，请下达最后的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.65,0:02:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.99,0:02:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加速素粒子炮，准备射击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.42,0:02:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准备射击!\N加速素粒子炮展开射角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.29,0:02:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,方位角4600
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.93,0:02:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,方位角4600
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.73,0:02:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加速粒子射线压100
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.17,0:02:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.10,0:02:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.26,0:03:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G战骑的诸位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.03,0:03:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请各位注意\N重力子能量的临界值
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.17,0:03:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一旦达到临界值\N合神会被强制解除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.21,0:03:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么的话\N我们将失去一切反击之力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.18,0:03:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人类的命运亦将自此画上休止符
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.71,0:03:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.78,0:03:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想不到外星异种这么顽强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.02,0:03:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琉菜、爱娜\N有没有吓坏了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.59,0:03:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才没有呢!\N人...人家有一点点啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.39,0:03:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回想一下模拟训练的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.09,0:03:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是有什么的话\N我会帮你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.86,0:03:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.96,0:03:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G战影...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.37,0:03:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会是谁在操控?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.00,0:03:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该不会是...绫香吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.07,0:04:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司 你干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.97,0:04:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还在战斗中哦!别这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.84,0:04:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑 谁要陪你们玩啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.93,0:05:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飞了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.77,0:05:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么机器人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.44,0:05:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.87,0:05:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重力子能量接近临界点了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.04,0:05:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经做好准备了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.71,0:05:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.55,0:05:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发射超重压力拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.47,0:05:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加速粒子炮命中目标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.57,0:05:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.54,0:05:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以后战斗由我们联合政府处理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.31,0:05:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你等一下可要\N好好的向我说明说明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.88,0:05:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.92,0:05:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总统先生 您看那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.36,0:06:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.60,0:06:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重力子能量达到临界值\N合神要被强制解除了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.60,0:06:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绫香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.35,0:06:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.62,0:06:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.50,0:06:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目标静默
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.54,0:06:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在被覆盖上外骨架般的壳后\N便失去动静了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.41,0:06:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂!这算是对待\N总统应有的态度吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.51,0:07:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们到底是什么人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.92,0:07:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天\N会重新正式向各位致意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.79,0:07:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位也请早一步\N回到自己的岗位比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.26,0:07:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.93,0:07:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我话还没有讲完
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.60,0:07:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个机器人\N是在哪里开发出来的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.90,0:07:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幕僚都集合了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.34,0:07:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 都已经在官邸集合了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.77,0:07:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别这样 浑蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.18,0:07:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干什么呀，住手...\N色女，花痴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.68,0:07:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂!给我乖一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.85,0:07:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要确定您是不是有哪里不舒服\N不这么仔细的检查怎么行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.65,0:07:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇!别这样!\N不要碰那里啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.19,0:07:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很有精神嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.79,0:07:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本没有检查的必要嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.13,0:07:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各、各位...请不要太过粗暴......
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.40,0:07:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手!别这样啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.27,0:07:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.82,0:08:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啊 大叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.82,0:08:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这位是葛莱茵．桑德曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.29,0:08:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是雷文，是桑德曼先生的副手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.52,0:08:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,葛莱茵．桑德曼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.73,0:08:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是你啊!绫香信上写的\N城堡的城主就是你呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.21,0:08:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绫香在哪里 把姊姊还给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.65,0:08:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不得无礼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.75,0:08:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,浑蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.55,0:08:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那封信是我寄给你的\N红英司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.49,0:08:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.99,0:08:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟着我来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.96,0:08:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为你介绍一下本城
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.40,0:09:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼，刚刚的G战影\N究竟是谁...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.17,0:09:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等晚点再说吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.14,0:09:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的\N重要的事情老是都不肯说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.25,0:09:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G强袭机\N重力子安定指数82%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.29,0:09:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重钻机，重粒子中和作业完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.73,0:09:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,攻击机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.49,0:09:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能量筒不足
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.29,0:09:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请从弹药库追加补充
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.33,0:09:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们是地球战骑队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.63,0:09:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地球战骑队?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.34,0:09:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是由我所创设\N要自外星异种的威胁下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.54,0:09:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保护人类的组织
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.84,0:09:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟是何方神圣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.61,0:09:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要操控这些机械
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.35,0:09:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,体内必须要拥有所谓的\N"G因子"这种特殊的酵素才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.32,0:09:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊?G..什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.42,0:09:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就想成是\N对于体内的重力异常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.76,0:09:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拥有的先天性耐力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.19,0:09:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.20,0:10:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有你\N都是G因子的拥有者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.47,0:10:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.97,0:10:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G攻击机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.67,0:10:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们选定你为\N这架战机的驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.34,0:10:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并为了引诱你主动来到这座城堡\N而假造了这封信，让你上当
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.62,0:10:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实只是想让你搭上攻击机\N确认一下你适不适合而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.76,0:10:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没想到才正要开始试验\N外星异种就来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.03,0:10:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对于用了这么不完美的方式\N这一点我得向你致歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.64,0:10:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过，我想，即使说明了原因\N还是没办法得到你的谅解吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.91,0:10:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像这种智慧超越人类的怪物\N竟然会找上人类下手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.58,0:10:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.18,0:10:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是骗人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.45,0:10:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直以来，绫香无论什么事\N都会对我说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.79,0:11:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她不可能瞒着我\N跑到这种奇怪的地方工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.19,0:11:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任何人都有表里两面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.86,0:11:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就找绫香出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.73,0:11:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她在这里吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.37,0:11:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直接问她，就一拍两瞪眼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.87,0:11:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她失踪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.84,0:11:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她在训练中失踪了\N至今我们都还没有找到她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.28,0:11:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们也是很担心的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.38,0:11:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种话!我会相信吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.85,0:11:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.52,0:11:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星异种再度开始行动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.40,0:11:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又行动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.53,0:11:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全体进入战斗位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.44,0:11:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不会出动的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.21,0:11:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.27,0:11:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要战斗的话，随便派个人去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.11,0:11:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这跟我没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.18,0:11:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有G因子拥有者的话\N机械是无法正常运转的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.01,0:12:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就只有你才能驾驶的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.82,0:12:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果一定要我驾驶的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.15,0:12:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就把绫香交出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.29,0:12:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样我就去驾驶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.62,0:12:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.93,0:12:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.23,0:12:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然他这么害怕，就饶过他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.03,0:12:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算少了他一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.80,0:12:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还是可以协助大家\N一起作战的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.24,0:12:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂!等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.07,0:12:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是因为害怕才这么说的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.84,0:12:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用逞强也没关系嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.01,0:12:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你跟我不一样，你太弱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.51,0:12:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你乖乖的在这里等着吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.41,0:12:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说...说我太弱~~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.12,0:12:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个浑蛋...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.36,0:12:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.62,0:12:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的确，就算多了个胆小鬼\N也只会碍手碍脚而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.59,0:12:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是说啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.00,0:12:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家的性命已经危在旦夕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.50,0:12:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是放了那种藉故开溜\N既胆小又没种的家伙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.04,0:12:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.77,0:13:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就干给你们看!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.34,0:13:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的没问题吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.24,0:13:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要勉强自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.88,0:13:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你别多管闲事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.88,0:13:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这、这算什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.92,0:13:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,棺材?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.49,0:13:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是进入重战机组的运送柜\N我先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.86,0:13:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也要出动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.36,0:13:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么怪癖好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.23,0:13:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少啰唆，快点坐进去啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.24,0:13:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.74,0:13:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很有意思的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.44,0:13:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然聒噪了点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.74,0:13:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是个值得锻炼的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.99,0:13:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本就不是对手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.12,0:13:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这头怪物...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.56,0:13:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次就要你好看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.90,0:14:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经觉悟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.94,0:14:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看我的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.91,0:14:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G战骑的诸位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.18,0:14:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,启动合神!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.88,0:14:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工学型态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.18,0:14:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重合神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.30,0:15:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重力子反应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.77,0:15:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安定指数90%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.04,0:15:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各机组正常运作中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.01,0:15:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距临界点还有9988点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.65,0:15:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱娜，你是我们女仆的代表\N加油哦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.85,0:15:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裘伊露，不要私下交谈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.42,0:15:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,型态已经变了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.99,0:16:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们是会进化的机械生命体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.39,0:16:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该是想到新的作战方式了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.00,0:16:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开始攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.30,0:16:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.97,0:16:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.05,0:16:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.65,0:16:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙什么东西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.95,0:16:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,力量、速度跟刚刚都不同嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.29,0:16:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.72,0:16:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说它又进化了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.07,0:16:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做得不错嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.55,0:17:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敌方转换为远距离攻击了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.52,0:17:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样岂不是老挨打吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.29,0:17:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道没什么武器吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.23,0:17:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 打中了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.83,0:17:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,攻击机座舱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.53,0:17:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,指挥由我来负责
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.27,0:17:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要任意行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.27,0:17:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么口气啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.55,0:17:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.48,0:17:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重力安定指数降至70%以下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.68,0:17:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,急速接近临界状态\N这样很危险的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.23,0:17:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是被那招直接攻击的话\N那就惨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.86,0:17:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们也有射击武器啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.63,0:17:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脚部武器齐射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.04,0:17:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司 一边说\N超重火神炮发射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.57,0:18:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一边按下右边红色按钮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.38,0:18:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,红..红色?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.84,0:18:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,武器操作系统是采\N语音与按钮同步进行系统
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.35,0:18:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说什么来着?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.18,0:18:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飞弹发射?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.72,0:18:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊!那个是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.89,0:18:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是飞弹，是火神炮啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.16,0:18:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且不是左边，是右边!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.16,0:18:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重火神炮发射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.13,0:18:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞定了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.20,0:18:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,定你个头啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.74,0:18:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这大白痴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.58,0:18:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重雷射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.55,0:18:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重飞弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.55,0:18:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.75,0:18:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G重钻机，超重压力拳\N准备射击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.63,0:18:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.21,0:19:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.15,0:19:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,压力拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.00,0:19:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.57,0:19:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然把拳头给打出去\N...真是乱搞一通嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.27,0:19:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重力子循环达到临界点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.68,0:19:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爷，请快点呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.05,0:19:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重弧光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.77,0:20:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星异种，被彻底歼灭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.65,0:20:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星异种
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.41,0:20:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有超重神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.85,0:20:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或许人类正同时遭到两大威胁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.36,0:20:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手!不要这样啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.46,0:20:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我乖一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.36,0:20:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要好好的检查才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.07,0:20:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过，我好高兴哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.84,0:20:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你愿意留在城里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.10,0:20:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是为了你们哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.11,0:20:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要找到绫香\N我马上就会闪人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.51,0:20:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个不要脱啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.65,0:20:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以说 连你都不知道\NG战影的事情吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.58,0:20:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是谁在操控的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.42,0:21:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他一定有很缜密的心思吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.19,0:21:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们也只能相信他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.80,0:21:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又让你多了一个难过的经历
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.17,0:21:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.85,0:21:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看着在烈阳热气下\N道路的那一方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.50,0:21:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,形形色色的事物\N呈现形形色色的摆动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.57,0:21:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知该为何这般\N心头思绪纷乱不已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.21,0:22:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但就这么视而不见\N朝向明日飞去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.76,0:22:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为无法接受如此的不成熟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.09,0:22:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才说出了这么不客气的话语
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.47,0:22:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若只是孤单一人地强出头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.17,0:22:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,换来的只有误解\N矛盾与迷惑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.17,0:22:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由于那牵系着悲伤的羁绊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.28,0:22:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让微笑的双眸中渗出了泪水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.88,0:22:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多想将这暖意传送出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.52,0:22:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,便紧握着手一直不愿放开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.49,0:22:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好让这祈祷得以传达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.00,0:22:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了!布丽姬妲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.37,0:22:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爷跟英司少爷不见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.34,0:22:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗?亚娘\N他们俩野到哪里去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.61,0:22:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下回播出"迷宫"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.47,0:23:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下周，各位的和平\N也将由我们来照料喔!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.86,0:23:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,机器人动画的真．王道传说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.56,0:23:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将所有肇始，化作原点\N因而诞生的终极神话，此刻...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.34,0:23:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,导演:大张正己\N作品:饿狼传说(TVVlRUS)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.09,0:23:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,角色设计:宇能诚\N作品:爱姬(TV 纯情房东俏房客)
